 2019-13012019-09-04,  ,  ,  ,  PS, 
ActAvoiding Complicity in Mistreatment by Foreign Entities Act
SubjectAvoiding Complicity in Mistreatment by Foreign Entities ** Director of the Financial Transactions and Reports Analysis Centre of Canada as the deputy head of that Centre, Commissioner of Revenue as the deputy head of the Canada Revenue Agency and the Clerk of the Privy Council as the deputy head of the Privy Council Office **
PrecisOrder designating the Director of the Financial Transactions and Reports Analysis Centre of Canada as the deputy head of that Centre, the Commissioner of Revenue as the deputy head of the Canada Revenue Agency and the Clerk of the Privy Council as the deputy head of the Privy Council Office for the purposes of the AVOIDING COMPLICITY IN MISTREATMENT BY FOREIGN ENTITIES ACT, in order to demonstrate the Government's commitment to make Canada's information sharing regime more transparent, consistent, and accountable, and enhance oversight on a government-wide basis.
